    title: "Fostering Teenagers as an Older Adult: Why Teens Often Thrive With You",
    excerpt: "Teens in foster care are the hardest group to place, but they often do best with grandparent-aged foster parents. Here is why and how to start.",
    category: "tips-tricks",
